image,pic,picture.description: Sends a random picture of a cat!

collection,cattos,c.description: Shows your cat collection! If a rarity is specified, your collection for that specific rarity will be shown.

daily.description: Claims your daily reward! Refreshes after 24 hours.

dex,catinfo,catdex.description: Displays information about the specified cat!

disable.description: Toggles whether or not you get cats from sending messages.

feed,f.description: Random chance to receive the specified cat!

leaderboard,leaderboards,lb.description: Shows the global leaderboard of who has the most money!

money,cash.description: Shows how much money you have!

parameters: The cat you wish to feed, or the keyword **'all'**.
The amount you wish to sell. If no amount is specified then all of the specified cat will be sold.

chance.description: Shows the chances of receiving each rarity of cat.

help.description: Gives info about the specified command.

invite.description: Sends the link to add **Cats o' Mighty** to your server!

settings.description: Sets the bot settings for the server (Manage Server permissions needed).
parameters:
**`show`** - message won't delete
**`hidden`** - messages won't show
**`disappear`** - messages will delete after 6 seconds

ping,pong.description: Shows the latency between Discord and the bot

supportserver,server,support.description: Sends the link to join the official **Cats o' Mighty** Support Server!

vote.description: Sends the link to vote for **Cats o' Mighty**! For voting, you will receive a random cat and a random amount of money!

addcat,ac.description: **Admin Command**. Adds cats to the selected persons account.
parameters: Optional. The account to add the cats to. If omitted, the cats will be added to the account of whoever issued the command.

addmoney,am.description: **Admin Command**. Adds cats to the selected persons account.
parameters: Optional. The account to add money to. If omitted, the money will be added to the account of whoever issued the command.

clearcats,cc.description: **Admin Command**. Adds cats to the selected persons account.
parameters: Optional. The account to have their cats cleared. If omitted, the cats will be cleard from the account of whoever issued the command.

stop.description: **Admin Command**. Kills the bot. You monster!

userinfo,userdata.description: **Admin Command**. Displays the specified user's Cats o' Mighty statistics.
parameters: The account to get the data for.
